Good Grips Food Mill
<b>Good Grips Food Mill:</b>
*Includes 3 stainless-steel discs for preparing foods of fine, medium, and coarse textures
*Stainless-steel inner bowl accommodates hot foods and prevents staining
*Unique release button makes it easy to exchange discs and disassemble for storage
*Three non-slip legs hold the Food Mill securely over bowls and pots up to 11 inches in diameter
*Measures 11 inches in diameter, holds 2 3/10 quarts
*All parts are dishwasher-safe

